org.youscope.addon.celldetection

Interface CellVisualizationAddonFactory


  • public interface CellVisualizationAddonFactory
    A factory to create cell detection addons. All implementations should export themselves with the help of Java's service loader technology.
    Author:
    Moritz Lang

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      CellVisualizationAddon createCellVisualizationAddon(java.lang.String ID)
      Returns a new Cell Visualization Addon for the given ID, or null if this factory does not support addons with the given ID.
      java.lang.String[] getCellVisualizationAddonIDs()
      Returns a list of all Cell Visualization Addon IDs types supported by this factory.
      boolean supportsCellVisualizationAddonID(java.lang.String ID)
      Returns true if this factory supports Cell Visualization Addons with the given ID, false otherwise.

    • Method Detail

      • createCellVisualizationAddon

        CellVisualizationAddon createCellVisualizationAddon(java.lang.String ID)
        Returns a new Cell Visualization Addon for the given ID, or null if this factory does not support addons with the given ID.
        Parameters:
        ID - The ID for which a Cell Visualization Addon should be created.
        Returns:
        New Addon.

      • getCellVisualizationAddonIDs

        java.lang.String[] getCellVisualizationAddonIDs()
        Returns a list of all Cell Visualization Addon IDs types supported by this factory.
        Returns:
        List of supported Cell Visualization Addons.

      • supportsCellVisualizationAddonID

        boolean supportsCellVisualizationAddonID(java.lang.String ID)
        Returns true if this factory supports Cell Visualization Addons with the given ID, false otherwise.
        Parameters:
        ID - The ID of the Cell Visualization Addon for which it should be queried if this factory supports it.
        Returns:
        True if this factory supports addons with the given ID, false otherwise.
